.. code:: console

   $ git-wshow --help
   Usage: git-wshow [-r REMOTE] [-a N] [-A] [-p] COMMIT

   Options:
     -r REMOTE   use this remote
     -a N        abbreviate hash to N digits (or more)
     -A          use alternative URL
     -p          only print the URL
     -h, --help  show this help message and exit

   $ git show 823091df626b74cf
   commit 823091df626b74cfa3542fa6d4eecdee6a1b3c08
   Author: Jakub Wilk <jwilk@jwilk.net>
   Date:   2021-11-26 11:53:31 +0100
